        <item>
            <title>iPhone 15 Pro Max 成本增　中国产零件成本占比跌至 2.5%</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/22/iphone-15-teardown-reveals-10-costlier/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-15-teardown-reveals-10-costlier</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/22/iphone-15-teardown-reveals-10-costlier/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 08:40:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1200763</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 每年推出新的 iPhone，其成本和使用的零件都会成为话题。早前 Nikkei 拆解了 iPhone 15 系列进行分析，发现当中使用的零件成本继续上升，而来自中国厂商的零件则比之前减少。<br /><span id="more-1200763"></span></p><p>据 Nikkei 的报告显示，与去年的型号相比，iPhone 15 Pro Max 的成本上涨了约 10%，连续两年创下最高水平，也使 iPhone 的净利润有所减少，不过他们预计明年将会加价，将增加的成本转嫁至消费者。成本的上升主要来自全球供应链和原材料成本的上升，包括晶片和电池等都变得更昂贵。尤其是采用钛合金的边框和望远镜头各自贵了 43% 和 280%。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/https3A2F2Fcms-image-bucket-production-ap-northeast-1-a7d2.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com2Fimages2F_aliases2Farticleimage2F42F92F42F12F46701494-1-eng-GB2F20231020-iPhone-cost-breakdown-by-country-Bar.png.jpeg" alt="" width="769" height="460" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1200765" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/https3A2F2Fcms-image-bucket-production-ap-northeast-1-a7d2.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com2Fimages2F_aliases2Farticleimage2F42F92F42F12F46701494-1-eng-GB2F20231020-iPhone-cost-breakdown-by-country-Bar.png.jpeg 769w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/https3A2F2Fcms-image-bucket-production-ap-northeast-1-a7d2.s3.ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com2Fimages2F_aliases2Farticleimage2F42F92F42F12F46701494-1-eng-GB2F20231020-iPhone-cost-breakdown-by-country-Bar.png-694x415.jpeg 694w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 769px" /></p><p>除了成本上升外，报告亦发现以成本计算，iPhone 15 Pro Max 采用了比上代更多的美国、台湾和南韩零件，来自中国厂商的零件则减少，其中中国厂商的组件占比跌至 2.5%，也就是除了作为装嵌地之外，并没有从 iPhone 销售中获益太多。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Technology/iPhone-15-teardown-reveals-10-costlier-parts-than-2022-flagship">Nikkei</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
